Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:08.65,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:10.99,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:15.62,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}What should I do{\fncinnamon cake}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:21.20,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}I forgot who I was before I met you
