Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:32.09,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Kicking the slope,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.17,0:00:35.89,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}a frail shadow stretches on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.89,0:00:40.85,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It's like a neverending summer break
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:46.35,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It feels like sneaking into a pool
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:51.36,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Hey, let's just swim with our clothes on
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:52.57,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Hop{\fncinnamon cake}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:55.40,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}A spiral of sensational temptation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.40,0:00:59.78,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Those beats that sting me are strange
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:03.25,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}They burn out and disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:05.41,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}I'm fine with those crazy days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:06.17,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Dress up
