Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.80,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}What's that dance called{\fncinnamon cake}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.80,0:01:13.88,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}It won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.88,0:01:23.35,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Don't go, it lingers on  in my ears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:26.35,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5\fad(150,150)}Melody is
