Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:00.18,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Fukahori Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.47,0:02:03.56,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Second year, class six, seat number twenty-two.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.06,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,So she's a year ahead of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.31,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She moved here from Tokyo during her first year of middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:11.90,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Her hobbies are oil painting and fencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:13.82,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Her birthday is February 10th.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.28,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.32,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Just for your information...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.57,0:02:18.70,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talkin' about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.11,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.53,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This has gotten as hard as a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.53,0:02:26.79,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,When you think about her, you get a lump in your throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.96,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,so you can't get the food down, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:32.63,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:35.25,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're completely lovesick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.76,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,L-Love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.30,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is what love is?{What is love? Baby don't hurt me...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:41.39,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you've never fallen in love before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.85,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:44.26,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're kiddin' me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:46.31,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.44,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If he actually falls for that girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:53.81,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he won't get between Ritsu and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:59.82,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we'll skip jazz after school today and meet up to formulate a plan, instead.
