Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:05.49,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? At my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.33,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,We ain't gonna go to Ri'ko's basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:10.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be able to relax more at home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.25,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:18.26,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we went to Ritsu's place, it's possible she would overhear us talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.76,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.55,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,But this is Ritsu's shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.51,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It's a row house, so Ri'ko's place is connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:28.93,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:30.35,Default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:33.19,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Bro! You're back early today, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.36,Default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Play with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:36.19,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, hold on. Where's Ma? {Typical Catholics. So many kids...}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:39.57,Default,Sachiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, Bro's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:38.94,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:42.32,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doin'? Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:50.45,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Ma, this is Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.16,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.38,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you always looking out for Sentaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.58,0:03:57.50,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're too kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:00.97,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy. Dig in, Richie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:06.51,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't have an appetite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.10,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can {\i1}always{\i0} eat watermelon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.48,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro loves his watermelon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:15.60,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,He told me he wasn't hungry, which is pretty strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:19.48,Default,Ma,0000,0000,0000,,but I just knew watermelon would do the trick, so I iced one up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:20.74,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:22.49,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro! Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.95,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Taichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:25.78,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,We found a weird bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.70,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A bug?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.78,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.78,0:04:28.70,Default,Taichi,0000,0000,0000,,It's over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:32.25,Default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, if you plant a watermelon seed, will it grow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:33.46,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Let's plant one an' see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:34.83,Default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.96,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.79,Default,Kota,0000,0000,0000,,It flew!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:41.46,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh, don't cry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.22,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,A group date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:48.80,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The four of us will go, including Ritsu and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.47,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you two started things off alone, she'd be on her guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:54.14,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh. I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:57.06,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you'll be the one to invite Miss Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.90,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point if you're not the one who does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.32,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.32,0:05:03.07,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't got it in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:04.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:06.95,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.32,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.33,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.45,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,My girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.49,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.46,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.96,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're in a bad mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:19.00,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Cute, ain't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.30,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Her full name is Sarah Vaughan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:22.63,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,A pigeon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:25.30,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Sarah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:26.84,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You're really agitated today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:29.30,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.30,0:05:32.60,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Since you keep talkin' about another girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.48,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.94,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm suddenly enjoying myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.11,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That was so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.24,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.45,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.08,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:01.17,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.59,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Who goes up to the girl and then runs away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:03.96,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.42,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,The note! The note!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.13,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.63,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.51,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:16.18,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,for suddenly interrupting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.44,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free this weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:26.19,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to take this opportunity to cult...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:27.49,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Cult...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.61,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,"Cultivate."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:31.49,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Cultivate our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:31.49,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.33,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:35.12,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.83,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,She agreed! She says she'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:41.13,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to Rendezvous Rock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:42.92,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Should I pack us a lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:47.05,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:49.80,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Just something light like rice balls would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:52.05,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:55.18,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, just so I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:59.69,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Which of you two is inviting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.69,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.98,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:06.07,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,He insisted on inviting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.40,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:09.19,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:10.70,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:13.70,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.99,0:07:15.49,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You said okay to a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:17.20,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.79,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.96,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It was going so smoothly and then you blew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:26.55,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I dunno why I said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:29.80,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Turn back time for me, Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.93,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,As if I could?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:35.68,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.14,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:42.14,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened to your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:44.69,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just another one of Sentaro's fights...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:46.94,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.28,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:51.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,We actually have one more person joining us today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.24,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:53.57,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.24,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Making lunch took longer than I thought it would...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.54,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're the girl who was getting harassed back at the beach...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:04.17,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.13,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You remember her, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.54,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, today— {emdash}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:11.13,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:13.80,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,The one with the glasses invited me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.55,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Are you all right?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.68,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru did?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.30,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.76,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What the heck are you doing?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.77,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay for a newcomer like me to intrude?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.77,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Get up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.43,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:24.40,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,The more the merrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.40,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's wrong with you today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.19,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.69,0:08:30.61,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, so it was Kaoru who asked her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:38.62,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:41.91,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,{\in1}Kaoru must have a weakness for pretty faces...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.29,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.92,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:47.21,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that your hat is really stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:48.78,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.13,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I wore it, I would still look like a hick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.13,0:08:54.17,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.93,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.18,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsu, when did you change your hairstyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:07.15,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika did it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:07.90,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:10.19,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It looks super. Really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.53,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:21.20,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told your family owns a record shop, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.00,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.21,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like jazz, Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:31.25,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,These two practice playing jazz music together just about every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.21,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,They play jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:37.80,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Kaoru plays piano and Sentaro is on drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.34,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,That's really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.51,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I know some people who listen to jazz,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.97,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,but this is my first time meeting anyone who actually plays it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:47.06,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,My two big brothers like jazz, so I listen too, once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:50.86,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,My brothers frown and furrow their brows a bit while they listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.36,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,but I prefer music that really hits you with a bang, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.82,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.82,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear you play the drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.24,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Y-You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.75,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I still, uh... stink at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:09.21,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you know you can't get better at music unless you have an audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.75,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let me hear you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.46,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is an unexpected development.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.38,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:19.76,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! I think I got scratched by a branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.56,0:10:27.48,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.27,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's got it after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:35.82,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Say, I heard a rumor that couples who climb together
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.90,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,to the top of that rock will get married some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.32,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,No girl's gonna get up that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.32,0:10:43.20,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie, you up for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.28,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.70,0:10:47.50,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm not letting you get away with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.37,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I can climb that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.79,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Would anyone like to go with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.38,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:56.21,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.42,0:11:03.05,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the sign says it's off limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.14,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:06.47,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.14,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I really wanted to see the view from up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:18.36,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have wolfed it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.62,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Those two seem to be hitting it off pretty well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:28.20,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru... You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:30.16,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.42,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to pick some flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Probably the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:41.22,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Boy, this rice ball is huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:04.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:08.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hurt Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.04,0:12:11.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the cruelest of ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:16.21,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I made the girl who's most important to me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.21,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those shoulders look so sad, but I have no right
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:22.97,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to try to comfort her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:36.02,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.44,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:39.27,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Richie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:42.07,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come with me a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.78,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This! This handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:50.04,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Yurika gave it to me as an apology for my towel yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.91,0:12:53.41,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,It smells kind of nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.67,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it my imagination?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.17,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:08.22,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.47,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can't pick up this handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:13.18,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just can't bear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:22.44,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,If you're here for this, you can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.07,0:13:24.86,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I was in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:26.70,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:29.12,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talkin' about?! Spill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.58,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:33.29,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're satisfied as long as you have this handkerchief, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:36.00,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Go home and sniff it all you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:37.96,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:39.96,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,You lookin' to start a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.42,0:13:44.34,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:47.51,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro, let go of Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.51,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.31,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get rough with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.85,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You owe Kaoru an apology!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:55.39,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.52,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I don't owe that guy nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.40,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:04.53,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You can't forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.86,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,This handkerchief is important to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:15.95,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:20.92,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Sentaro is drumming away like a madman right about now. {;D}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.71,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,"Richie, you stupid idiot!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:24.17,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.38,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier to make up if you do it early on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.34,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.47,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:36.68,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, before you moved here, Sentaro always practiced alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:40.19,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Shutting himself up in the basement, not letting anyone near him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:43.94,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Even I didn't feel welcome down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:49.15,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,But ever since you came, Kaoru, that feeling's disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:53.03,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm positive he was happy to find a friend he could play jazz with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.96,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Kaoru, should I guess what you two were fighting about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:03.08,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You like Yurika, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:07.96,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So you got mad at Sentaro for showing off that handkerchief...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.26,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,She is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:15.22,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd been born looking like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.52,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.14,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Ritsu, you're plenty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:22.73,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,a-attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.40,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for trying to cheer me up, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:31.36,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.82,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:34.28,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wasn't trying to cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:35.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.99,0:15:39.29,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.00,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.50,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ritsu! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:50.26,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me out, Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.92,Default,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's the ruckus, Ritsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:50.26,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,Drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.01,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I-I didn't come here to see you. {B-baka!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.89,0:16:03.73,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.73,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:14.49,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,He has the same feelings for the girl he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:28.59,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't just join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.17,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.59,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't joinin' in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.48,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's following along again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.24,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.45,Default,Sen,0000,0000,0000,,Festival jazz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.20,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! I can't play if I'm laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:37.41,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, maybe I'll play something just for Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:40.08,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.20,0:17:43.54,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}maybe I'll try letting her know how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.92,0:17:50.20,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Sentaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.17,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.80,Default,Yurika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't be so stiff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:04.89,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:08.14,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}hell is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.90,0:18:15.78,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure Ritsu is thinking about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:21.95,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Meanwhile, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:26.66,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Ritsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:31.00,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,There's a song that I'd like to play for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:36.39,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Actually, I wanted to practice the song a little more first...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.93,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I feel like I have to play it for her right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:42.01,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This piece I've secretly been practicing my heart out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.27,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Play through me, Bill Evans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:12.56,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,"Someday My Prince Will Come."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:15.40,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,That's the title of the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.57,0:20:20.40,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,So are you the prince, Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.03,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:25.41,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,You've been practicing for Yurika, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:28.33,Default,Ritsuko,0000,0000,0000,,And this is your dress rehearsal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.25,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.96,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.71,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one that I like...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.55,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to give me an answer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:51.98,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to let you know that there's somebody here 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.60,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,who's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.47,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ritsu has eyes for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:06.70,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's always on her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.33,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still, that doesn't bother me at all right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:16.12,Default,Kaoru,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You taught me that it was possible to fall in love like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:21.09,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:28.76,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I waited for you on that road downhill
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:41.98,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}Our promise to meet after school always held a goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:51.28,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}I was weak and distorted, and seemed to easily crack under pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:22:03.88,ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(250,250)}You were the one who gave me wings then
